      "html": "\n<style data-kid=\"0\">\n  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap');\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n  body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: #ffffff; color: #0c1e35; }\n</style>\n\n<nav style=\"background:#ffffff; border-bottom:1px solid #e2e6eb; height:64px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; padding:0 64px;\" data-kid=\"1\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:20px; font-weight:800; color:#0c1e35; letter-spacing:-0.5px;\" data-kid=\"2\">LION <span style=\"font-weight:300; font-size:13px; color:#5a6a7e; letter-spacing:1px;\" data-kid=\"3\">ENGINEERING</span></div>\n  <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; gap:36px;\" data-kid=\"4\">\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:500; color:#5a6a7e; text-decoration:none; letter-spacing:0.2px;\" data-kid=\"5\">Startseite</a>\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:500; color:#5a6a7e; text-decoration:none; letter-spacing:0.2px;\" data-kid=\"6\">Leistungen</a>\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:500; color:#5a6a7e; text-decoration:none; letter-spacing:0.2px;\" data-kid=\"7\">Über uns</a>\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#1a6dd4; text-decoration:none; letter-spacing:0.2px; border-bottom:2px solid #1a6dd4; padding-bottom:2px;\" data-kid=\"8\">Karriere</a>\n    <div style=\"width:1px; height:16px; background:#e2e6eb;\" data-kid=\"9\"></div>\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#ffffff; background:#1a6dd4; padding:10px 20px; border-radius:4px; text-decoration:none; letter-spacing:0.2px;\" data-kid=\"10\">Kontakt</a>\n    <span style=\"font-size:12px; color:#0c1e35; letter-spacing:0.3px; font-weight:600;\" data-kid=\"11\">DE&nbsp;|&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#5a6a7e; font-weight:400;\" data-kid=\"130\">EN</span></span>\n  </div>\n</nav>\n\n<section style=\"position:relative; min-height:600px; display:flex; align-items:center; overflow:hidden; background:#091627;\" data-kid=\"12\">\n  <img src=\"https://images.pexels.com/photos/6285142/pexels-photo-6285142.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1440&q=80\" alt=\"Ingenieurteam bei der Überprüfung technischer Pläne\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"position:absolute; inset:0; width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; object-position:center;\" data-kid=\"13\">\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; inset:0; background:linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(9,22,39,0.92) 0%, rgba(9,22,39,0.65) 55%, rgba(9,22,39,0.2) 100%);\" data-kid=\"14\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:relative; z-index:2; padding:96px 96px 96px 96px; max-width:660px;\" data-kid=\"15\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:12px; font-weight:700; color:#d4881a; letter-spacing:1.5px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:20px;\" data-kid=\"16\">WERDEN SIE TEIL UNSERES TEAMS</p>\n    <h1 style=\"font-size:56px; font-weight:800; color:#ffffff; line-height:1.08; letter-spacing:-1px; margin-bottom:24px;\" data-kid=\"17\">Gestalten Sie die Zukunft<br data-kid=\"18\">des Engineerings</h1>\n    <p style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:300; color:#b8c4d4; line-height:1.6; max-width:480px; margin-bottom:40px;\" data-kid=\"19\">Wir suchen Ingenieure, die technische Tiefe mit Leidenschaft für Präzision verbinden. Arbeiten Sie an echten Luft- und Raumfahrt- sowie Automotive-Projekten – gemeinsam mit erfahrenen Spezialisten.</p>\n    <a href=\"#positions\" style=\"display:inline-block; font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#ffffff; background:#1a6dd4; padding:14px 28px; border-radius:4px; text-decoration:none; letter-spacing:0.2px;\" data-kid=\"20\">Offene Stellen ansehen</a>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#ffffff; padding:96px 0;\" data-kid=\"21\">\n  <div style=\"max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 96px; display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:80px;\" data-kid=\"22\">\n    <div style=\"flex-shrink:0; min-width:120px;\" data-kid=\"23\">\n      <span style=\"font-size:96px; font-weight:800; color:#d4881a; line-height:1; opacity:0.25; display:block;\" data-kid=\"24\">01</span>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex:1; padding-top:12px;\" data-kid=\"25\">\n      <h2 style=\"font-size:22px; font-weight:700; color:#0c1e35; margin-bottom:16px; letter-spacing:-0.3px;\" data-kid=\"26\">Anspruchsvolle Projekte</h2>\n      <p style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:#2d3a4a; line-height:1.6; max-width:640px; margin-bottom:24px;\" data-kid=\"27\">Arbeiten Sie an echten Luft- und Raumfahrt- und Automotive-Projekten für Kunden wie Airbus, BMW und Magna. Jeder Auftrag bringt von Beginn an echte Engineering-Verantwortung.</p>\n      <div style=\"display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px;\" data-kid=\"28\">\n        <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#5a6a7e; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;\" data-kid=\"29\"><span style=\"width:4px; height:4px; border-radius:50%; background:#d4881a; flex-shrink:0; display:inline-block;\" data-kid=\"30\"></span>Airbus H145/H175 Strukturprogramme</span>\n        <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#5a6a7e; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;\" data-kid=\"31\"><span style=\"width:4px; height:4px; border-radius:50%; background:#d4881a; flex-shrink:0; display:inline-block;\" data-kid=\"32\"></span>BMW EV Antriebsstrangintegration</span>\n        <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#5a6a7e; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;\" data-kid=\"33\"><span style=\"width:4px; height:4px; border-radius:50%; background:#d4881a; flex-shrink:0; display:inline-block;\" data-kid=\"34\"></span>IABG Qualifikationskampagnen</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#f6f7f9; padding:96px 0;\" data-kid=\"35\">\n  <div style=\"max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 96px; display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:80px;\" data-kid=\"36\">\n    <div style=\"flex-shrink:0; min-width:120px;\" data-kid=\"37\">\n      <span style=\"font-size:96px; font-weight:800; color:#d4881a; line-height:1; opacity:0.25; display:block;\" data-kid=\"38\">02</span>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex:1; padding-top:12px;\" data-kid=\"39\">\n      <h2 style=\"font-size:22px; font-weight:700; color:#0c1e35; margin-bottom:16px; letter-spacing:-0.3px;\" data-kid=\"40\">Karriereentwicklung</h2>\n      <p style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:#2d3a4a; line-height:1.6; max-width:640px; margin-bottom:24px;\" data-kid=\"41\">Lion investiert in Ihre Entwicklung. Wir unterstützen Fachzertifizierungen, Konferenzteilnahmen und internes Mentoring durch Senior-Ingenieure mit 20+ Jahren Erfahrung in der Luft- und Raumfahrt.</p>\n      <div style=\"display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px;\" data-kid=\"42\">\n        <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#5a6a7e; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;\" data-kid=\"43\"><span style=\"width:4px; height:4px; border-radius:50%; background:#d4881a; flex-shrink:0; display:inline-block;\" data-kid=\"44\"></span>CATIA V5/V6 Schulungen</span>\n        <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#5a6a7e; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;\" data-kid=\"45\"><span style=\"width:4px; height:4px; border-radius:50%; background:#d4881a; flex-shrink:0; display:inline-block;\" data-kid=\"46\"></span>EASA-Regelwerkskurse</span>\n        <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#5a6a7e; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;\" data-kid=\"47\"><span style=\"width:4px; height:4px; border-radius:50%; background:#d4881a; flex-shrink:0; display:inline-block;\" data-kid=\"48\"></span>Direkte Projektverantwortung</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#ffffff; padding:96px 0;\" data-kid=\"49\">\n  <div style=\"max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 96px; display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:80px;\" data-kid=\"50\">\n    <div style=\"flex-shrink:0; min-width:120px;\" data-kid=\"51\">\n      <span style=\"font-size:96px; font-weight:800; color:#d4881a; line-height:1; opacity:0.25; display:block;\" data-kid=\"52\">03</span>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex:1; padding-top:12px;\" data-kid=\"53\">\n      <h2 style=\"font-size:22px; font-weight:700; color:#0c1e35; margin-bottom:16px; letter-spacing:-0.3px;\" data-kid=\"54\">Attraktive Konditionen</h2>\n      <p style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:#2d3a4a; line-height:1.6; max-width:640px; margin-bottom:24px;\" data-kid=\"55\">Wir bieten faire, am Münchner Luftfahrtmarkt orientierte Gehälter, flexible Arbeitsmodelle und eine Teamkultur, die auf gegenseitigem Respekt und technischer Exzellenz basiert.</p>\n      <div style=\"display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px;\" data-kid=\"56\">\n        <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#5a6a7e; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;\" data-kid=\"57\"><span style=\"width:4px; height:4px; border-radius:50%; background:#d4881a; flex-shrink:0; display:inline-block;\" data-kid=\"58\"></span>Wettbewerbsfähiges Münchner Gehalt</span>\n        <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#5a6a7e; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;\" data-kid=\"59\"><span style=\"width:4px; height:4px; border-radius:50%; background:#d4881a; flex-shrink:0; display:inline-block;\" data-kid=\"60\"></span>Hybrides Arbeiten</span>\n        <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#5a6a7e; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;\" data-kid=\"61\"><span style=\"width:4px; height:4px; border-radius:50%; background:#d4881a; flex-shrink:0; display:inline-block;\" data-kid=\"62\"></span>Kleines Team, große Wirkung</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"positions\" style=\"background:#ffffff; padding:96px 0; border-top:1px solid #e2e6eb;\" data-kid=\"63\">\n  <div style=\"max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 96px;\" data-kid=\"64\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:12px; font-weight:700; color:#d4881a; letter-spacing:1.5px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"65\">OFFENE STELLEN</p>\n    <h2 style=\"font-size:28px; font-weight:700; color:#0c1e35; margin-bottom:48px; letter-spacing:-0.3px;\" data-kid=\"66\">Verstärken Sie unser Ingenieurteam</h2>\n\n    <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:2fr 2fr 1.5fr 140px; padding:0 0 16px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #e2e6eb;\" data-kid=\"67\">\n      <span style=\"font-size:12px; font-weight:700; color:#5a6a7e; letter-spacing:0.5px; text-transform:uppercase;\" data-kid=\"68\">Position</span>\n      <span style=\"font-size:12px; font-weight:700; color:#5a6a7e; letter-spacing:0.5px; text-transform:uppercase;\" data-kid=\"69\">Fachbereich</span>\n      <span style=\"font-size:12px; font-weight:700; color:#5a6a7e; letter-spacing:0.5px; text-transform:uppercase;\" data-kid=\"70\">Standort</span>\n      <span data-kid=\"71\"></span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:2fr 2fr 1.5fr 140px; padding:24px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #e2e6eb; align-items:center;\" data-kid=\"72\">\n      <span style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:600; color:#2d3a4a;\" data-kid=\"73\">Berechnungsingenieur (m/w/d)</span>\n      <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#5a6a7e;\" data-kid=\"74\">Luft- und Raumfahrt · FEM/Strukturen</span>\n      <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#5a6a7e;\" data-kid=\"75\">Ottobrunn</span>\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#1a6dd4; text-decoration:none; text-align:right;\" data-kid=\"76\">Bewerben →</a>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:2fr 2fr 1.5fr 140px; padding:24px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #e2e6eb; align-items:center;\" data-kid=\"77\">\n      <span style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:600; color:#2d3a4a;\" data-kid=\"78\">Konstruktionsingenieur (m/w/d)</span>\n      <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#5a6a7e;\" data-kid=\"79\">Luft- und Raumfahrt · CATIA V5</span>\n      <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#5a6a7e;\" data-kid=\"80\">Ottobrunn</span>\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#1a6dd4; text-decoration:none; text-align:right;\" data-kid=\"81\">Bewerben →</a>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:2fr 2fr 1.5fr 140px; padding:24px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #e2e6eb; align-items:center;\" data-kid=\"82\">\n      <span style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:600; color:#2d3a4a;\" data-kid=\"83\">Projektleiter (m/w/d)</span>\n      <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#5a6a7e;\" data-kid=\"84\">Luft- und Raumfahrt · Systeme</span>\n      <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#5a6a7e;\" data-kid=\"85\">Ottobrunn</span>\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#1a6dd4; text-decoration:none; text-align:right;\" data-kid=\"86\">Bewerben →</a>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:2fr 2fr 1.5fr 140px; padding:24px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #e2e6eb; align-items:center;\" data-kid=\"87\">\n      <span style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:600; color:#2d3a4a;\" data-kid=\"88\">Systemintegrationsingenieur (m/w/d)</span>\n      <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#5a6a7e;\" data-kid=\"89\">Automotive · Integration</span>\n      <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#5a6a7e;\" data-kid=\"90\">Ottobrunn</span>\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#1a6dd4; text-decoration:none; text-align:right;\" data-kid=\"91\">Bewerben →</a>\n    </div>\n\n    <p style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:300; color:#5a6a7e; margin-top:32px; line-height:1.6;\" data-kid=\"92\">Kein passendes Profil? Wir freuen uns über Initiativbewerbungen an <a href=\"mailto:karriere@lion-engineering.de\" style=\"color:#1a6dd4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"93\">karriere@lion-engineering.de</a></p>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#0c1e35; padding:80px 96px; text-align:center;\" data-kid=\"94\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:12px; font-weight:700; color:#d4881a; letter-spacing:1.5px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:16px;\" data-kid=\"95\">INITIATIVBEWERBUNG</p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:28px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff; margin-bottom:16px; letter-spacing:-0.3px;\" data-kid=\"96\">Kein passendes Angebot gefunden?</h2>\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:#b8c4d4; max-width:480px; margin:0 auto 32px; line-height:1.6;\" data-kid=\"97\">Senden Sie uns Ihren Lebenslauf und erzählen Sie uns, wie Sie zum Team beitragen möchten.</p>\n  <a href=\"#\" style=\"display:inline-block; font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#ffffff; background:#1a6dd4; padding:14px 28px; border-radius:4px; text-decoration:none; letter-spacing:0.2px;\" data-kid=\"98\">Bewerbung senden</a>\n</section>\n\n<footer style=\"background:#0c1e35; padding:64px 96px 32px;\" data-kid=\"99\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:20px; font-weight:800; color:#ffffff; letter-spacing:-0.5px; margin-bottom:8px;\" data-kid=\"100\">LION <span style=\"font-weight:300; font-size:13px; color:#b8c4d4; letter-spacing:1px;\" data-kid=\"101\">ENGINEERING</span></div>\n  <p style=\"font-size:13px; font-weight:400; color:#b8c4d4; margin-bottom:48px;\" data-kid=\"102\">Ottobrunn · München · EN 9100 zertifiziert</p>\n  <div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr; gap:48px; padding-bottom:48px; border-bottom:1px solid #132d4f;\" data-kid=\"103\">\n    <div data-kid=\"104\">\n      <p style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff; margin-bottom:20px; letter-spacing:0.2px;\" data-kid=\"105\">Unternehmen</p>\n      <div style=\"display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px;\" data-kid=\"106\">\n        <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#b8c4d4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"107\">Über Lion</a>\n        <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#b8c4d4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"108\">Zertifizierungen</a>\n        <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#b8c4d4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"109\">Karriere</a>\n        <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#b8c4d4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"110\">Aktuelles</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div data-kid=\"111\">\n      <p style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff; margin-bottom:20px; letter-spacing:0.2px;\" data-kid=\"112\">Leistungen</p>\n      <div style=\"display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px;\" data-kid=\"113\">\n        <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#b8c4d4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"114\">Luft- und Raumfahrt</a>\n        <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#b8c4d4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"115\">Automotive</a>\n        <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#b8c4d4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"116\">Technologie</a>\n        <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#b8c4d4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"117\">Beratung</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div data-kid=\"118\">\n      <p style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff; margin-bottom:20px; letter-spacing:0.2px;\" data-kid=\"119\">Kontakt</p>\n      <div style=\"display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px;\" data-kid=\"120\">\n        <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#b8c4d4;\" data-kid=\"121\">Einsteinstr. 10</span>\n        <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#b8c4d4;\" data-kid=\"122\">85521 Ottobrunn, DE</span>\n        <a href=\"tel:+4989614657200\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#b8c4d4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"123\">+49 89 6146572-0</a>\n        <a href=\"mailto:info@lion-engineering.de\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#b8c4d4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"124\">info@lion-engineering.de</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; padding-top:24px;\" data-kid=\"125\">\n    <span style=\"font-size:13px; font-weight:400; color:#b8c4d4;\" data-kid=\"126\">© 2026 Lion Engineering GmbH. Alle Rechte vorbehalten.</span>\n    <div style=\"display:flex; gap:24px;\" data-kid=\"127\">\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:13px; font-weight:400; color:#b8c4d4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"128\">Impressum</a>\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:13px; font-weight:400; color:#b8c4d4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"129\">Datenschutz</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</footer>\n",
