      "html": "\n<style data-kid=\"0\">\n  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap');\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n  body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: #ffffff; color: #0c1e35; }\n</style>\n\n<nav style=\"background:#ffffff; border-bottom:1px solid #e2e6eb; height:64px; display:flex; align-items:center; padding:0 24px; justify-content:space-between;\" data-kid=\"1\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:800; color:#0c1e35; letter-spacing:-0.5px;\" data-kid=\"2\">LION<span style=\"color:#1a6dd4;\" data-kid=\"3\">.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:5px; cursor:pointer;\" data-kid=\"4\">\n    <span style=\"display:block; width:24px; height:2px; background:#0c1e35; border-radius:1px;\" data-kid=\"5\"></span>\n    <span style=\"display:block; width:24px; height:2px; background:#0c1e35; border-radius:1px;\" data-kid=\"6\"></span>\n    <span style=\"display:block; width:16px; height:2px; background:#0c1e35; border-radius:1px;\" data-kid=\"7\"></span>\n  </div>\n</nav>\n\n<section style=\"position:relative; min-height:400px; display:flex; align-items:flex-end; overflow:hidden;\" data-kid=\"8\">\n  <img src=\"https://images.pexels.com/photos/30841308/pexels-photo-30841308.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800&q=80\" alt=\"Detailansicht der Helikopter-Rotormechanik\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"position:absolute; inset:0; width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; object-position:center;\" data-kid=\"9\">\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; inset:0; background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(9,22,39,0.3) 0%, rgba(9,22,39,0.95) 100%);\" data-kid=\"10\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:relative; z-index:1; padding:40px 24px;\" data-kid=\"11\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#d4881a; letter-spacing:1.5px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"12\">LEISTUNGEN</p>\n    <h1 style=\"font-size:32px; font-weight:800; color:#ffffff; line-height:1.12; letter-spacing:-0.5px; margin-bottom:16px;\" data-kid=\"13\">Luft- und Raumfahrttechnik</h1>\n    <p style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:#b8c4d4; line-height:1.6;\" data-kid=\"14\">Primär- und Sekundärstrukturen, Simulation, Systemintegration und Projektmanagement für die Luft- und Raumfahrtindustrie.</p>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#ffffff;\" data-kid=\"15\">\n  <div style=\"height:240px; overflow:hidden;\" data-kid=\"16\">\n    <img src=\"https://images.pexels.com/photos/13316850/pexels-photo-13316850.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600&q=80\" alt=\"Nahaufnahme von Flugzeugstruktur-Nieten\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover;\" data-kid=\"17\">\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:40px 24px;\" data-kid=\"18\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#d4881a; letter-spacing:1.5px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"19\">STRUKTURAUSLEGUNG</p>\n    <h2 style=\"font-size:20px; font-weight:700; color:#0c1e35; line-height:1.3; margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"20\">Primär- und Sekundärstrukturen</h2>\n    <p style=\"font-size:15px; font-weight:300; color:#2d3a4a; line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:20px;\" data-kid=\"21\">Auslegung und Analyse von Rumpf, Spanten, Halterungen und Verbundstrukturen für Dreh- und Starrflügler.</p>\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#1a6dd4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"22\">Mehr erfahren →</a>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#f6f7f9;\" data-kid=\"23\">\n  <div style=\"height:240px; overflow:hidden;\" data-kid=\"24\">\n    <img src=\"https://images.pexels.com/photos/3862149/pexels-photo-3862149.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600&q=80\" alt=\"Ingenieure bei der FEM-Simulationsarbeit\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover;\" data-kid=\"25\">\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:40px 24px;\" data-kid=\"26\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#d4881a; letter-spacing:1.5px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"27\">BERECHNUNG &amp; SIMULATION</p>\n    <h2 style=\"font-size:20px; font-weight:700; color:#0c1e35; line-height:1.3; margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"28\">FEM-Analyse &amp; Lastfälle</h2>\n    <p style=\"font-size:15px; font-weight:300; color:#2d3a4a; line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:20px;\" data-kid=\"29\">Ermüdungs-, statische und dynamische Strukturanalysen mit branchenüblichen Tools. Nachweise gemäß EASA CS-27/29 und LTH.</p>\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#1a6dd4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"30\">Mehr erfahren →</a>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#ffffff;\" data-kid=\"31\">\n  <div style=\"height:240px; overflow:hidden;\" data-kid=\"32\">\n    <img src=\"https://images.pexels.com/photos/3913017/pexels-photo-3913017.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600&q=80\" alt=\"Ingenieur am CAD-Arbeitsplatz\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover;\" data-kid=\"33\">\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:40px 24px;\" data-kid=\"34\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#d4881a; letter-spacing:1.5px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"35\">SYSTEMINTEGRATION</p>\n    <h2 style=\"font-size:20px; font-weight:700; color:#0c1e35; line-height:1.3; margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"36\">Avionik &amp; mechanische Systeme</h2>\n    <p style=\"font-size:15px; font-weight:300; color:#2d3a4a; line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:20px;\" data-kid=\"37\">Integration von Hydraulik-, Elektro- und Mechanik-Systemen in die Flugzeugstruktur. Schnittstellenmanagement mit Zulieferern.</p>\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#1a6dd4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"38\">Mehr erfahren →</a>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#f6f7f9;\" data-kid=\"39\">\n  <div style=\"height:240px; overflow:hidden;\" data-kid=\"40\">\n    <img src=\"https://images.pexels.com/photos/30841298/pexels-photo-30841298.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600&q=80\" alt=\"Detailansicht der Helikopter-Montage\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover;\" data-kid=\"41\">\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:40px 24px;\" data-kid=\"42\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#d4881a; letter-spacing:1.5px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"43\">PROZESSENGINEERING</p>\n    <h2 style=\"font-size:20px; font-weight:700; color:#0c1e35; line-height:1.3; margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"44\">Fertigungs- und Montageprozesse</h2>\n    <p style=\"font-size:15px; font-weight:300; color:#2d3a4a; line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:20px;\" data-kid=\"45\">Definition und Optimierung von Fertigungsprozessen für Luftfahrtkomponenten inkl. Quality-Gates und Betriebsmittelkonzept.</p>\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#1a6dd4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"46\">Mehr erfahren →</a>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#ffffff;\" data-kid=\"47\">\n  <div style=\"height:240px; overflow:hidden;\" data-kid=\"48\">\n    <img src=\"https://images.pexels.com/photos/3862373/pexels-photo-3862373.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600&q=80\" alt=\"Ingenieure bei der Überprüfung technischer Dokumentation\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover;\" data-kid=\"49\">\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:40px 24px;\" data-kid=\"50\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#d4881a; letter-spacing:1.5px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"51\">QUALIFIKATION &amp; DOKUMENTATION</p>\n    <h2 style=\"font-size:20px; font-weight:700; color:#0c1e35; line-height:1.3; margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"52\">Musterprüfungsunterstützung</h2>\n    <p style=\"font-size:15px; font-weight:300; color:#2d3a4a; line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:20px;\" data-kid=\"53\">Erstellung von Zulassungsdokumentation, Prüfplänen und Qualifikationsberichten nach EASA- und FAA-Anforderungen.</p>\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#1a6dd4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"54\">Mehr erfahren →</a>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#f6f7f9;\" data-kid=\"55\">\n  <div style=\"height:240px; overflow:hidden;\" data-kid=\"56\">\n    <img src=\"https://images.pexels.com/photos/6285157/pexels-photo-6285157.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600&q=80\" alt=\"Ingenieure im Projektbesprechung\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover;\" data-kid=\"57\">\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"padding:40px 24px;\" data-kid=\"58\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#d4881a; letter-spacing:1.5px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"59\">PROJEKTMANAGEMENT</p>\n    <h2 style=\"font-size:20px; font-weight:700; color:#0c1e35; line-height:1.3; margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"60\">Technische Projektleitung</h2>\n    <p style=\"font-size:15px; font-weight:300; color:#2d3a4a; line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:20px;\" data-kid=\"61\">Ganzheitliches Projektmanagement für Engineering-Pakete – Steuerung von Umfang, Terminen und Schnittstellen mit OEM-Projektteams.</p>\n    <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#1a6dd4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"62\">Mehr erfahren →</a>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"height:240px; overflow:hidden;\" data-kid=\"63\">\n  <img src=\"https://images.pexels.com/photos/5493554/pexels-photo-5493554.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800&q=80\" alt=\"Detailansicht der Triebwerksturbine eines Großflugzeugs\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; object-position:center 40%;\" data-kid=\"64\">\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#0c1e35; padding:48px 0 0;\" data-kid=\"65\">\n  <div style=\"padding:0 24px 32px;\" data-kid=\"66\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:11px; font-weight:700; color:#d4881a; letter-spacing:1.5px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:12px;\" data-kid=\"67\">UNSERE LEISTUNGEN</p>\n    <h2 style=\"font-size:24px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff; line-height:1.2;\" data-kid=\"68\">Weitere Kompetenzbereiche</h2>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"position:relative; height:280px; overflow:hidden;\" data-kid=\"69\">\n    <img src=\"https://images.pexels.com/photos/19233057/pexels-photo-19233057.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600&q=80\" alt=\"Hochmoderne Roboter-Montagelinie in der Automobilindustrie\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover;\" data-kid=\"70\">\n    <div style=\"position:absolute; inset:0; background:linear-gradient(to top, rgba(9,22,39,0.88) 0%, rgba(9,22,39,0.2) 50%, transparent 100%);\" data-kid=\"71\"></div>\n    <div style=\"position:absolute; bottom:32px; left:24px;\" data-kid=\"72\">\n      <h3 style=\"font-size:20px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff; margin-bottom:10px;\" data-kid=\"73\">AUTOMOTIVE</h3>\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; opacity:0.85;\" data-kid=\"74\">Entdecken →</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"position:relative; height:280px; overflow:hidden;\" data-kid=\"75\">\n    <img src=\"https://images.pexels.com/photos/5506047/pexels-photo-5506047.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600&q=80\" alt=\"Modernes Engineering-Technologielabor\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover;\" data-kid=\"76\">\n    <div style=\"position:absolute; inset:0; background:linear-gradient(to top, rgba(9,22,39,0.88) 0%, rgba(9,22,39,0.2) 50%, transparent 100%);\" data-kid=\"77\"></div>\n    <div style=\"position:absolute; bottom:32px; left:24px;\" data-kid=\"78\">\n      <h3 style=\"font-size:20px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff; margin-bottom:10px;\" data-kid=\"79\">TECHNOLOGIE</h3>\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; opacity:0.85;\" data-kid=\"80\">Entdecken →</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section style=\"background:#0c1e35; padding:64px 24px; text-align:center; border-top:1px solid #132d4f;\" data-kid=\"81\">\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:24px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff; margin-bottom:24px; line-height:1.3;\" data-kid=\"82\">Lassen Sie uns Ihre Anforderungen besprechen</h2>\n  <a href=\"#\" style=\"display:block; background:#1a6dd4; color:#ffffff; font-size:14px; font-weight:600; padding:16px 28px; border-radius:4px; text-decoration:none; letter-spacing:0.2px;\" data-kid=\"83\">Kontakt aufnehmen</a>\n</section>\n\n<footer style=\"background:#0c1e35; padding:48px 24px 0;\" data-kid=\"84\">\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom:48px;\" data-kid=\"85\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:800; color:#ffffff; letter-spacing:-0.3px; margin-bottom:16px;\" data-kid=\"86\">LION<span style=\"color:#1a6dd4;\" data-kid=\"87\">.</span></div>\n    <p style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:300; color:#b8c4d4; line-height:1.6;\" data-kid=\"88\">Präzisions-Engineering für Luft- und Raumfahrt sowie Automotive – aus Ottobrunn bei München.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom:32px;\" data-kid=\"89\">\n    <h4 style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff; margin-bottom:16px;\" data-kid=\"90\">Leistungen</h4>\n    <div style=\"display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px;\" data-kid=\"91\">\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#b8c4d4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"92\">Luft- und Raumfahrt</a>\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#b8c4d4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"93\">Automotive</a>\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:400; color:#b8c4d4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"94\">Technologie</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom:40px;\" data-kid=\"95\">\n    <h4 style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:#ffffff; margin-bottom:16px;\" data-kid=\"96\">Kontakt</h4>\n    <div style=\"display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px;\" data-kid=\"97\">\n      <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:300; color:#b8c4d4;\" data-kid=\"98\">Einsteinstr. 10, 85521 Ottobrunn</span>\n      <span style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:300; color:#b8c4d4;\" data-kid=\"99\">+49 89 6146572-0</span>\n      <a href=\"mailto:info@lion-engineering.de\" style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:300; color:#b8c4d4; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"100\">info@lion-engineering.de</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"border-top:1px solid #132d4f; padding:20px 0; text-align:center;\" data-kid=\"101\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px; color:#5a6a7e; margin-bottom:8px;\" data-kid=\"102\">© 2026 Lion Engineering GmbH</p>\n    <div style=\"display:flex; gap:20px; justify-content:center;\" data-kid=\"103\">\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:13px; color:#5a6a7e; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"104\">Impressum</a>\n      <a href=\"#\" style=\"font-size:13px; color:#5a6a7e; text-decoration:none;\" data-kid=\"105\">Datenschutz</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</footer>\n",
